  "_description": "Per-component presentation metadata consumed by jsonui-mcp-server. Augments attribute_definitions.json (which defines the raw attribute schema, including binding_direction per attribute) with human descriptions, aliases, platform availability, platform-specific implementation notes, and agent-facing rules. Edit this file to change what `lookup_component` / `search_components` / `lookup_attribute` return from the MCP.",
